let's have fun with it

00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:21.460 align:middle line:84%
for beginners and those
who've been in it for a while.

00:01:21.460 --> 00:01:23.940 align:middle line:84%
And what was your
initial introduction

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:26.989 align:middle line:84%
and fascinate-- into and
fascination with this world

00:01:26.989 --> 00:01:28.530 align:middle line:84%
that we're going to
be talking about?

00:01:28.530 --> 00:01:28.980 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL LEVY: Oh great.

00:01:28.980 --> 00:01:29.280 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.730 align:middle line:90%
That's a great question.

00:01:30.730 --> 00:01:34.620 align:middle line:10%
Well, in 1981 I had
a spiritual awakening

00:01:34.620 --> 00:01:38.430 align:middle line:10%
that came out of just intense
suffering based on a trauma

00:01:38.430 --> 00:01:39.630 align:middle line:10%
I had.

00:01:39.630 --> 00:01:44.010 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't understand
it then, but I now

00:01:44.010 --> 00:01:47.370 align:middle line:84%
have the language to see
that I was experiencing--

00:01:47.370 --> 00:01:49.690 align:middle line:84%
I was encountering
the quantum realm,

00:01:49.690 --> 00:01:51.780 align:middle line:90%
and it totally blew my mind.

00:01:51.780 --> 00:01:54.240 align:middle line:84%
Basically, it got me
in a lot of trouble,

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.070 align:middle line:84%
because I wasn't in
a container, so I

00:01:56.070 --> 00:01:58.620 align:middle line:84%
was so enthusiastic and
excited about what I

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:00.465 align:middle line:90%
was realizing that--

00:02:00.465 --> 00:02:02.430 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You alienated
everyone in your life.

00:02:02.430 --> 00:02:03.170 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Oh.

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:03.936 align:middle line:90%
Well, totally.

00:02:03.936 --> 00:02:04.720 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, I'm
just teasing you--

00:02:04.720 --> 00:02:05.370 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: No, but that's--

00:02:05.370 --> 00:02:06.120 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: --but that's
usually what follows.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.828 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: That's
absolutely what happened.

00:02:07.828 --> 00:02:10.830 align:middle line:84%
Within 24 hours, I got
locked up, and diagnosed,

00:02:10.830 --> 00:02:15.180 align:middle line:84%
and hospitalized, I was
medicated, and it was intense.

00:02:15.180 --> 00:02:17.066 align:middle line:84%
And during that
next 18 months, I

00:02:17.066 --> 00:02:19.440 align:middle line:84%
was probably hospitalized
about four or five other times.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:22.020 align:middle line:84%
And every single
time, I was guaranteed

00:02:22.020 --> 00:02:25.159 align:middle line:84%
that I had this mental illness,
this chemical imbalance,

00:02:25.159 --> 00:02:26.700 align:middle line:84%
that I would have
to be on medication

00:02:26.700 --> 00:02:27.850 align:middle line:90%
for the rest of my life.

00:02:27.850 --> 00:02:30.480 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that, you
know, these doctors

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.120 align:middle line:84%
had no idea what they were
talking about, because--

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:36.150 align:middle line:84%
and the thing is
that's what saved me,

00:02:36.150 --> 00:02:39.010 align:middle line:84%
that inner knowing,
because it was, you know,

00:02:39.010 --> 00:02:40.650 align:middle line:84%
subjectively my
experience was it

00:02:40.650 --> 00:02:44.340 align:middle line:84%
was really clear
that I was having

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:46.290 align:middle line:84%
some form of spiritual
awakening that couldn't

00:02:46.290 --> 00:02:48.540 align:middle line:90%
have been more obvious to me.

00:02:48.540 --> 00:02:50.910 align:middle line:84%
It's been made very clear
to me by my inner guidance

00:02:50.910 --> 00:02:52.810 align:middle line:84%
to not talk about a
lot of the experiences.

00:02:52.810 --> 00:02:55.890 align:middle line:84%
But there was one experience
that I have sort of been given

00:02:55.890 --> 00:02:59.700 align:middle line:84%
permission to talk about
from my inner guidance,

00:02:59.700 --> 00:03:01.470 align:middle line:84%
and it happened within
the first minute

00:03:01.470 --> 00:03:04.410 align:middle line:84%
of being put in the first
psychiatric hospital.

00:03:04.410 --> 00:03:07.560 align:middle line:84%
So here I was having this
full blown awakening.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:09.390 align:middle line:84%
I was I was
recognizing that this

00:03:09.390 --> 00:03:11.220 align:middle line:84%
is a collective
dream, that we're all

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:13.610 align:middle line:84%
dream characters in
each other's dreams,

00:03:13.610 --> 00:03:15.900 align:middle line:84%
and that we're all
interconnected and

00:03:15.900 --> 00:03:17.880 align:middle line:84%
interdependent, and
all those things.

00:03:17.880 --> 00:03:22.055 align:middle line:84%
And I was so enthusiastic
that I got put in an ambulance

00:03:22.055 --> 00:03:23.430 align:middle line:84%
and brought to
Highland Hospital.

00:03:23.430 --> 00:03:25.740 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: How did your
enthusiasm show itself that got

00:03:25.740 --> 00:03:26.550 align:middle line:90%
you locked up?

00:03:26.550 --> 00:03:28.290 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: Well, in
the sense that--

00:03:28.290 --> 00:03:29.199 align:middle line:90%
I was with a friend.

00:03:29.199 --> 00:03:31.740 align:middle line:84%
I was living in the Bay Area
and a friend from the East Coast

00:03:31.740 --> 00:03:35.490 align:middle line:84%
was visiting me, and he
knew a particular Paul that

00:03:35.490 --> 00:03:38.610 align:middle line:84%
is very stable and
conditioned, and sort

00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:42.840 align:middle line:84%
of this kind of like a
particular habitual Paul

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:43.950 align:middle line:90%
that he knew.

00:03:43.950 --> 00:03:46.410 align:middle line:84%
And it was like I had
this radical personality

00:03:46.410 --> 00:03:50.637 align:middle line:84%
change overnight, and he had
never seen anything like it.

00:03:50.637 --> 00:03:53.220 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So you shifted from
what to-- show us what it would

00:03:53.220 --> 00:03:53.980 align:middle line:90%
look like.

00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:54.480 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah, just from--

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:56.271 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You were
conditioned and normal.

00:03:56.271 --> 00:03:59.430 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: I was just like normal,
ordinary sense of identity

00:03:59.430 --> 00:04:02.280 align:middle line:90%
to just being filled--

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.720 align:middle line:90%
it was like being this--

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:07.120 align:middle line:84%
a light bulb that went from
75 watts to a trillion watts

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:07.920 align:middle line:90%
just like that.

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:08.880 align:middle line:90%
[SNAPPING FINGERS]

00:04:08.880 --> 00:04:12.690 align:middle line:84%
And the energy coming through
me was so over the top and--

00:04:12.690 --> 00:04:14.020 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Manic beyond--

00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:15.020 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Well, it just--

00:04:15.020 --> 00:04:16.829 align:middle line:84%
from the outside, it
appeared, you know,

00:04:16.829 --> 00:04:19.380 align:middle line:84%
because I now
understand, you know, oh,

00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:21.420 align:middle line:84%
it looked just like
somebody in a manic episode.

00:04:21.420 --> 00:04:21.930 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:04:21.930 --> 00:04:24.305 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: But to get to the
experience that one experience

00:04:24.305 --> 00:04:27.090 align:middle line:84%
that happens, so that's
why I was in the airport,

00:04:27.090 --> 00:04:29.640 align:middle line:84%
I was flying up to Seattle
from San Francisco.

00:04:29.640 --> 00:04:32.449 align:middle line:84%
We never made it on
the air-- on the plane,

00:04:32.449 --> 00:04:34.240 align:middle line:84%
because the police got
called and I got put

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:36.870 align:middle line:84%
in an ambulance to
Highland Hospital.

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:42.420 align:middle line:84%
And then within the first minute
of entering Highland Hospital--

00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:45.520 align:middle line:84%
I'll never forget this, it
radically changed my life--

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.250 align:middle line:84%
they bring me into
this lounge which

00:04:47.250 --> 00:04:50.640 align:middle line:84%
is where the psychiatric
patients were all hanging out,

00:04:50.640 --> 00:04:53.340 align:middle line:84%
and I'm in this
complete altered state.

00:04:53.340 --> 00:04:57.330 align:middle line:84%
And right away, I see this
woman and she's an older woman,

00:04:57.330 --> 00:05:01.370 align:middle line:84%
and her eyes-- you know,
she can't see, she's blind.

00:05:01.370 --> 00:05:02.730 align:middle line:90%
Her eyes are opaque.

00:05:02.730 --> 00:05:04.010 align:middle line:90%
It's very obvious.

00:05:04.010 --> 00:05:06.660 align:middle line:84%
And without even thinking
about what to do or say,

00:05:06.660 --> 00:05:09.210 align:middle line:84%
I feel really drawn to her
and I go right up to her,

00:05:09.210 --> 00:05:11.670 align:middle line:90%
and I just stare in her eyes.

00:05:11.670 --> 00:05:15.030 align:middle line:84%
And out of my mouth, as if
I was given a script to say,

00:05:15.030 --> 00:05:19.260 align:middle line:84%
came the words, all you have
to do to see is open your eyes

00:05:19.260 --> 00:05:20.440 align:middle line:90%
and look.

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:23.530 align:middle line:84%
And I kept on saying
those words over and over,

00:05:23.530 --> 00:05:25.570 align:middle line:90%
kept on getting closer to her.

00:05:25.570 --> 00:05:28.660 align:middle line:84%
The whole thing took maybe,
you know, one minute,

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:31.150 align:middle line:84%
and then by the
end of that minute,

00:05:31.150 --> 00:05:33.220 align:middle line:90%
she had regained her sight.

00:05:33.220 --> 00:05:37.420 align:middle line:84%
And it was as if it was this
choreography at that moment

00:05:37.420 --> 00:05:39.940 align:middle line:84%
they took me and they
strapped me up on a bed

00:05:39.940 --> 00:05:41.340 align:middle line:90%
where I spent the night.

00:05:41.340 --> 00:05:43.540 align:middle line:84%
And it was a little bit of
a weird night to put it--

00:05:43.540 --> 00:05:43.690 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Well, yeah.

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:44.940 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: I didn't
exactly get to sleep.

00:05:44.940 --> 00:05:45.550 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:05:45.550 --> 00:05:48.050 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: But then what happened,
just to complete the story,

00:05:48.050 --> 00:05:50.410 align:middle line:84%
then the next morning they
unstrapped me and they put me

00:05:50.410 --> 00:05:53.350 align:middle line:84%
in this room with
this woman, the same--

00:05:53.350 --> 00:05:56.080 align:middle line:84%
she's now ex-- an
ex-blind woman.

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:58.370 align:middle line:84%
And she's staring
at me-- not staring,

00:05:58.370 --> 00:06:01.210 align:middle line:84%
but she's smiling
from ear to ear at me

00:06:01.210 --> 00:06:02.860 align:middle line:90%
and she's not saying a word.

00:06:02.860 --> 00:06:04.330 align:middle line:84%
And I'm just sitting
there with her

00:06:04.330 --> 00:06:06.340 align:middle line:84%
and, all of a sudden,
my heart chakra

00:06:06.340 --> 00:06:09.490 align:middle line:84%
just blossomed, and I had never
had that experience before,

00:06:09.490 --> 00:06:11.680 align:middle line:84%
but it was like this
lotus petal, the 1,000

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:13.150 align:middle line:90%
petal lotus just blossomed.

00:06:13.150 --> 00:06:15.560 align:middle line:84%
And then I understood,
oh, I get it.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:19.180 align:middle line:84%
Her eyes were physically
fine, but psychologically,

00:06:19.180 --> 00:06:20.230 align:middle line:90%
she wasn't--

00:06:20.230 --> 00:06:22.870 align:middle line:84%
you know, she was just
not letting herself look.

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:26.200 align:middle line:84%
And somehow, I kind of,
whatever, psychically or

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:28.780 align:middle line:84%
clairvoyantly saw
that, and it was

00:06:28.780 --> 00:06:33.160 align:middle line:84%
if I was the person sent
by, you know, casting, the,

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:37.300 align:middle line:84%
you know, whatever just
to say those lines,

00:06:37.300 --> 00:06:40.510 align:middle line:84%
because she was ready to heal
her hysterical blindness.

00:06:40.510 --> 00:06:44.350 align:middle line:84%
And I saw that, oh, that's what
happened that night before.

00:06:44.350 --> 00:06:46.910 align:middle line:84%
And then she says to me, the
only words she ever said to me,

00:06:46.910 --> 00:06:49.420 align:middle line:84%
she goes, aren't you going
to answer the phone call from

00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:51.910 align:middle line:84%
and she mentions
my father's name.

00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:55.150 align:middle line:84%
And then within seconds, the
nurse comes into the room

00:06:55.150 --> 00:06:57.190 align:middle line:84%
and says, Paul, your
father's on the phone,

00:06:57.190 --> 00:06:58.930 align:middle line:84%
because my parents
had just gotten word

00:06:58.930 --> 00:07:02.390 align:middle line:84%
that I had a psychotic
break and was hospitalized.

00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:04.840 align:middle line:84%
And so I got out of that
hospital after three days,

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:07.240 align:middle line:84%
because the doctor in
charge, he convinced me

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:10.490 align:middle line:84%
I had to prove to him
that I wasn't crazy.

00:07:10.490 --> 00:07:13.490 align:middle line:84%
And so I heard that, and I just
immediately forced myself down

00:07:13.490 --> 00:07:14.290 align:middle line:90%
and began talking--

00:07:14.290 --> 00:07:15.400 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: To your
normal Paul position.

00:07:15.400 --> 00:07:16.540 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: To my normal Paul.

00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:17.350 align:middle line:90%
my--

00:07:17.350 --> 00:07:18.730 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Tell them
what they need to hear.

00:07:18.730 --> 00:07:19.688 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: The repressed.

00:07:19.688 --> 00:07:22.120 align:middle line:84%
Talking about my problems,
my guilt, my neuroses.

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:24.420 align:middle line:84%
And he says, oh, you're
totally normal, you can go.

00:07:24.420 --> 00:07:25.220 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:07:25.220 --> 00:07:28.060 align:middle line:84%
And I got together with him,
you know, one week after.

00:07:28.060 --> 00:07:30.790 align:middle line:84%
I called him up
and we had a meal.

00:07:30.790 --> 00:07:32.920 align:middle line:84%
And I told him about
the blind woman,

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:35.660 align:middle line:84%
and he got very uncomfortable
to talk about it.

00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:37.330 align:middle line:84%
But he said to me
the fact that I

00:07:37.330 --> 00:07:40.750 align:middle line:84%
was able to have the
fluidity between the states

00:07:40.750 --> 00:07:42.970 align:middle line:84%
and just step right into
being normal like that,

00:07:42.970 --> 00:07:45.860 align:middle line:84%
that was proof to him
that I wasn't crazy.

00:07:45.860 --> 00:07:49.330 align:middle line:84%
And the one final
thing, within a few days

00:07:49.330 --> 00:07:50.950 align:middle line:84%
of getting out of
that hospital, I

00:07:50.950 --> 00:07:54.490 align:middle line:84%
knew something totally
over the top was happening.

00:07:54.490 --> 00:07:57.120 align:middle line:84%
So I found out about there
was a monk in San Francisco,

00:07:57.120 --> 00:08:01.780 align:middle line:84%
this Buddhist monk from Myanmar
is what it's called now,

00:08:01.780 --> 00:08:03.247 align:middle line:90%
you know, the old Burma.

00:08:03.247 --> 00:08:05.080 align:middle line:84%
Told him what happened
with the blind woman.

00:08:05.080 --> 00:08:07.455 align:middle line:84%
He says, oh, you're in luck,
the greatest Buddhist master

00:08:07.455 --> 00:08:09.120 align:middle line:84%
of all of Burma
has just arrived,

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.150 align:middle line:90%
this 85-year-old master.

00:08:10.150 --> 00:08:12.322 align:middle line:84%
I went, and within
like a few days

00:08:12.322 --> 00:08:13.780 align:middle line:84%
of getting out of
the hospital, I'm

00:08:13.780 --> 00:08:16.090 align:middle line:84%
sitting at the feet of
the greatest Buddhist

00:08:16.090 --> 00:08:19.240 align:middle line:84%
master of Burma and
getting his blessings.

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:21.710 align:middle line:84%
And so my life was
never the same.

00:08:21.710 --> 00:08:22.510 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Clearly.

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:22.897 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah.

00:08:22.897 --> 00:08:25.120 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So now that
experience is loaded with all

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.140 align:middle line:90%
kinds of stuff.

00:08:26.140 --> 00:08:30.280 align:middle line:84%
Number one, you're being
was in trauma and suffering.

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:31.240 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Right.

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:33.220 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And
some aspect of you,

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:36.760 align:middle line:84%
combined with some
aspect of universe,

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:41.520 align:middle line:84%
stepped in, coalesced an
energy to blast through you

00:08:41.520 --> 00:08:44.960 align:middle line:84%
at an incredible wattage to
show you another reality.

