00:21:27.344 --> 00:21:29.760 align:middle line:84%
one way of understanding what
quantum physics was pointing

00:21:29.760 --> 00:21:33.600 align:middle line:84%
at was that before
quantum physics,

00:21:33.600 --> 00:21:36.430 align:middle line:84%
physics thought they were
studying an objective world--

00:21:36.430 --> 00:21:37.230 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:21:37.230 --> 00:21:40.050 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: --and they were just
passive observers and studying

00:21:40.050 --> 00:21:42.960 align:middle line:84%
this universe that was
separate from themselves.

00:21:42.960 --> 00:21:45.870 align:middle line:84%
