even something as

00:21:50.880 --> 00:21:55.230 align:middle line:84%
minuscule as an electron,
we change the electron,

00:21:55.230 --> 00:21:58.320 align:middle line:84%
we change ourselves, and we
change the whole universe

00:21:58.320 --> 00:22:01.140 align:middle line:90%
