reaction in a feedback loop

00:23:06.600 --> 00:23:11.490 align:middle line:84%
where you've taken this infinite
creative potential that's

00:23:11.490 --> 00:23:14.520 align:middle line:84%
inside of all of us and
you've just scaled it down

00:23:14.520 --> 00:23:16.380 align:middle line:90%
to such a minuscule--

00:23:16.380 --> 00:23:19.320 align:middle line:84%
