subject if I'm having

00:23:46.020 --> 00:23:47.880 align:middle line:90%
relationship to an object.

00:23:47.880 --> 00:23:52.050 align:middle line:84%
And if there's no object,
all of a sudden, who am I?

00:23:52.050 --> 00:23:53.646 align:middle line:84%
So you see, that's
where, in my book,

00:23:53.646 --> 00:23:55.020 align:middle line:84%
