00:24:19.740 --> 00:24:23.010 align:middle line:84%
us up at the same time, and it's
like this feedback loop that's

00:24:23.010 --> 00:24:26.170 align:middle line:84%
not linear, but it's like
this circular feedback loop.

00:24:26.170 --> 00:24:30.190 align:middle line:84%
It's acausal and atemporal,
