00:24:37.210 --> 00:24:38.880 align:middle line:84%
you begin to realize,
wait a second,

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:41.290 align:middle line:84%
things aren't
quite as they seem.

00:24:41.290 --> 00:24:44.970 align:middle line:84%
