and sort of in this normal way,

00:24:44.970 --> 00:24:47.280 align:middle line:84%
like ordinary reality,
then you begin

00:24:47.280 --> 00:24:50.040 align:middle line:84%
to realize, wait a second, there
is like, you know, this field,

00:24:50.040 --> 00:24:53.730 align:middle line:84%
this non-local field which
physics talks about that

00:24:53.730 --> 00:24:57.720 align:middle line:84%
actually contains and expresses
itself through everything

00:24:57.720 --> 00:24:58.600 align:middle line:90%
that's happening.

00:24:58.600 --> 00:25:03.300 align:middle line:84%
And in that field, matter and
our minds are not separate.

00:25:03.300 --> 00:25:07.170 align:middle line:84%
Because quantum physics
discovered that consciousness

00:25:07.170 --> 00:25:08.930 align:middle line:84%
