of quantum physics.

00:28:32.862 --> 00:28:34.320 align:middle line:84%
And that was my
first introduction,

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:37.140 align:middle line:84%
so I never got into it in
a classical point of view.

00:28:37.140 --> 00:28:40.770 align:middle line:84%
I was only brought into
it once the first books

00:28:40.770 --> 00:28:46.020 align:middle line:84%
