emerging on the con--

00:28:46.020 --> 00:28:49.000 align:middle line:84%
I guess the marriage of
consciousness and physics,

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:51.780 align:middle line:84%
the marriage of, as
you say, the logos

00:28:51.780 --> 00:28:54.720 align:middle line:84%
and the chaos or prima
materia from which

00:28:54.720 --> 00:28:56.160 align:middle line:90%
all things are created.

00:28:56.160 --> 00:28:57.750 align:middle line:84%
And I found-- I
mean, it was-- to me,

00:28:57.750 --> 00:29:00.750 align:middle line:84%
it was really a mind
altering experience to read

00:29:00.750 --> 00:29:01.980 align:middle line:90%
that book the first time.

00:29:01.980 --> 00:29:02.550 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Right, right.

00:29:02.550 --> 00:29:05.008 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And then of course,
