of our lives.

00:29:26.940 --> 00:29:27.180 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah.

00:29:27.180 --> 00:29:29.620 align:middle line:84%
Well, the thing about
quantum physics-- two things.

00:29:29.620 --> 00:29:33.210 align:middle line:84%
On the one hand,
it pervades our day

00:29:33.210 --> 00:29:36.617 align:middle line:84%
to day everyday, you know, just
existence, just ordinary life.

00:29:36.617 --> 00:29:37.950 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It's the basis of it.

00:29:37.950 --> 00:29:38.783 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Absolutely.

00:29:38.783 --> 00:29:40.860 align:middle line:84%
So it's not some sort
of esoteric thing

00:29:40.860 --> 00:29:44.100 align:middle line:84%
that's, oh, this higher
dimensional abstract, you know,

00:29:44.100 --> 00:29:45.130 align:middle line:90%
contemplation.

00:29:45.130 --> 00:29:48.690 align:middle line:84%
It's something that is informing
every moment of our lives.

00:29:48.690 --> 00:29:50.880 align:middle line:84%
The thing I want to
not forget to say,

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:55.240 align:middle line:84%
and it feels really important
to say, these two other things.

00:29:55.240 --> 00:29:58.860 align:middle line:84%
One is quantum
physics is showing us

00:29:58.860 --> 00:29:59.910 align:middle line:90%
