00:29:59.910 --> 00:30:02.460 align:middle line:84%
It's showing us the dreamlike
nature of this reality,

00:30:02.460 --> 00:30:03.940 align:middle line:84%
and that's what
the book is about.

00:30:03.940 --> 00:30:06.090 align:middle line:84%
The second thing is
that quantum physics,

00:30:06.090 --> 00:30:08.995 align:middle line:84%
and really this
is an edge, but it

00:30:08.995 --> 00:30:10.620 align:middle line:84%
feels really important
to say quantum--

00:30:10.620 --> 00:30:15.870 align:middle line:84%
what quantum physics is actually
pointing at and it's actually,

00:30:15.870 --> 00:30:19.440 align:middle line:84%
you know, revealing to
us it's the solution

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:22.710 align:middle line:84%
for the world for the
multiple crises in our world.

00:30:22.710 --> 00:30:24.300 align:middle line:84%
If people-- if more
and more people

00:30:24.300 --> 00:30:28.450 align:middle line:84%
understand what quantum physics
is actually pointing at,

00:30:28.450 --> 00:30:30.000 align:middle line:90%
it can change the world.

00:30:30.000 --> 00:30:32.700 align:middle line:84%
But the thing about
its insights is

00:30:32.700 --> 00:30:34.800 align:middle line:84%
that say if, you
know, the two of us

00:30:34.800 --> 00:30:36.570 align:middle line:84%
or a few people,
if we understand--

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:38.430 align:middle line:84%
and even to use
the word understand

