this viral way that can
ignite a spiritual awakening

00:31:09.270 --> 00:31:11.040 align:middle line:84%
in our species that
we haven't even been

00:31:11.040 --> 00:31:13.200 align:middle line:90%
able to imagine up until now.

00:31:13.200 --> 00:31:14.610 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, I
