with the media, especially

00:43:51.320 --> 00:43:52.120 align:middle line:90%
mainstream media.

00:43:52.120 --> 00:43:52.440 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Oh, totally.

00:43:52.440 --> 00:43:52.940 align:middle line:90%
With the propaganda.

00:43:52.940 --> 00:43:53.690 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: For example--

00:43:53.690 --> 00:43:54.250 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah, yeah, totally.

00:43:54.250 --> 00:43:55.720 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --the Propaganda.

00:43:55.720 --> 00:44:00.640 align:middle line:84%
And so our mass psychology has
become from a top down level,

00:44:00.640 --> 00:44:03.280 align:middle line:84%
from governments,
militaries, and so forth,

