predict and control.

00:44:04.600 --> 00:44:07.430 align:middle line:84%
Very old-- dysfunctional
patriarchal attitude--

00:44:07.430 --> 00:44:08.230 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Right.

00:44:08.230 --> 00:44:11.500 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: --that has really
gained a lot of stickiness

00:44:11.500 --> 00:44:13.777 align:middle line:84%
for thousands of years
and become concretized.

00:44:13.777 --> 00:44:14.860 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:44:14.860 --> 00:44:16.750 align:middle line:84%
And that's where like
these physicists--

00:44:16.750 --> 00:44:19.690 align:middle line:84%
you see, it's so interesting
for me, as a non physicist,

00:44:19.690 --> 00:44:21.700 align:middle line:84%
