00:45:34.304 --> 00:45:35.220 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:45:35.220 --> 00:45:36.830 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: And that,
when I read that--

00:45:36.830 --> 00:45:38.670 align:middle line:84%
and they were also
saying, oh yeah,

00:45:38.670 --> 00:45:40.890 align:middle line:84%
we don't take any expert's
word for anything.

00:45:40.890 --> 00:45:43.060 align:middle line:84%
Experts are meaningless,
from our point of view.

00:45:43.060 --> 00:45:43.960 align:middle line:90%
We're all amateurs.

00:45:43.960 --> 00:45:44.760 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:45:44.760 --> 00:45:47.430 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: And that
point of view--

00:45:47.430 --> 00:45:49.830 align:middle line:84%
