they say there is
somebody who knows

00:45:54.420 --> 00:45:55.770 align:middle line:90%
where all the mistakes are--

00:45:55.770 --> 00:45:56.040 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:45:56.040 --> 00:45:56.670 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: --because
they've made them.

00:45:56.670 --> 00:45:56.990 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:45:56.990 --> 00:45:58.470 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: And that
really spoke to me.

00:45:58.470 --> 00:45:59.010 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:45:59.010 --> 00:45:59.970 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:45:59.970 --> 00:46:04.200 align:middle line:84%
You talk about, in this
process, of finding

00:46:04.200 --> 00:46:05.670 align:middle line:90%
our own capabilities.

00:46:05.670 --> 00:46:07.560 align:middle line:84%
You talk about
polishing the jewel.

00:46:07.560 --> 00:46:08.360 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:46:08.360 --> 00:46:09.193 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah, yeah.

00:46:09.193 --> 00:46:12.810 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So I'm assuming this
