00:47:06.900 --> 00:47:11.700 align:middle line:84%
degree, we add that much
light to our own consciousness

00:47:11.700 --> 00:47:15.180 align:middle line:84%
and that non-locally,
outside of space and time,

00:47:15.180 --> 00:47:17.860 align:middle line:84%
gets invested into
the whole universe,

00:47:17.860 --> 00:47:23.830 align:middle line:84%
or the whole universe lights up
via our act of self reflection.

00:47:23.830 --> 00:47:26.870 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And on that
