00:47:30.970 --> 00:47:31.770 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Right.

00:47:31.770 --> 00:47:34.680 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Most people
see them as either/or,

00:47:34.680 --> 00:47:36.250 align:middle line:90%
together or separate, right?

00:47:36.250 --> 00:47:37.050 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah.

00:47:37.050 --> 00:47:39.720 align:middle line:84%
The way to make change
in this universe

00:47:39.720 --> 00:47:43.380 align:middle line:84%
is-- yeah, it would be great
if the whole collectivity could

00:47:43.380 --> 00:47:47.130 align:middle line:84%
wake up, but is through the
individual, that any one of us

00:47:47.130 --> 00:47:50.610 align:middle line:84%
actually like having the
recognition of our nature,

00:47:50.610 --> 00:47:53.220 align:middle line:90%
of our true nature.

00:47:53.220 --> 00:47:55.590 align:middle line:84%
You know, like I was
saying, you know,

00:47:55.590 --> 00:47:58.500 align:middle line:84%
that immediately
the [INAUDIBLE],,

00:47:58.500 --> 00:48:01.290 align:middle line:90%
it informs the whole world.

00:48:01.290 --> 00:48:05.070 align:middle line:84%
And the thing which is
so interesting about that

00:48:05.070 --> 00:48:08.880 align:middle line:84%
is that one thought form
that's really inspiring

00:48:08.880 --> 00:48:11.490 align:middle line:84%
is that say if you have
this glass of water

00:48:11.490 --> 00:48:13.890 align:middle line:84%
and you put like a grain of
sugar in the glass of water,

00:48:13.890 --> 00:48:14.850 align:middle line:90%
it will just dissolve.

00:48:14.850 --> 00:48:16.225 align:middle line:84%
And you put a
second grain, it'll

00:48:16.225 --> 00:48:19.080 align:middle line:84%
just dissolve, and
on and on, until you

00:48:19.080 --> 00:48:21.150 align:middle line:90%
reach the point of saturation.

00:48:21.150 --> 00:48:24.030 align:middle line:84%
And once you reach
that saturation point,

00:48:24.030 --> 00:48:27.780 align:middle line:84%
you add one more grain of sugar
and a crystal will emerge.

00:48:27.780 --> 00:48:31.860 align:middle line:84%
And the point is is
that any one of us,

00:48:31.860 --> 00:48:34.770 align:middle line:84%
at even at this
moment, if we actually

00:48:34.770 --> 00:48:36.690 align:middle line:84%
have the recognition
of our nature,

00:48:36.690 --> 00:48:39.360 align:middle line:84%
we might be that
grain of sugar that

00:48:39.360 --> 00:48:43.200 align:middle line:84%
crystallizes a whole
awakening in our species.

00:48:43.200 --> 00:48:44.400 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: That's very true.

00:48:44.400 --> 00:48:45.960 align:middle line:84%
And as you say, the
process of being

00:48:45.960 --> 00:48:49.290 align:middle line:84%
able to honor that in one
another, make ourselves whole,

00:48:49.290 --> 00:48:52.380 align:middle line:84%
see the wholeness in others
actually reinforces itself,

00:48:52.380 --> 00:48:55.590 align:middle line:84%
just like in a dream, to make
the whole-- to make each of us

00:48:55.590 --> 00:48:57.007 align:middle line:90%
whole in this process.

00:48:57.007 --> 00:48:57.840 align:middle line:90%
>> PAUL: Yeah, yeah.

00:48:57.840 --> 00:49:01.530 align:middle line:84%
And the thing is we can only
see the wholeness in each other.

00:49:01.530 --> 00:49:02.721 align:middle line:90%
You see, I have a big--

00:49:02.721 --> 00:49:05.220 align:middle line:84%
I think it's the biggest chapter
in the whole book about how

00:49:05.220 --> 00:49:07.570 align:middle line:84%
quantum physics informs
our everyday relationships.

00:49:07.570 --> 00:49:08.370 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:49:08.370 --> 00:49:12.420 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: And to the extent that
if I see like say, for example,

00:49:12.420 --> 00:49:14.580 align:middle line:84%
with us, if I'm seeing
a shadow part of you

00:49:14.580 --> 00:49:16.740 align:middle line:84%
and I'm concretizing
that part of you, well,

00:49:16.740 --> 00:49:19.800 align:middle line:84%
then that's making it-- it's not
causing you to manifest in that

00:49:19.800 --> 00:49:22.770 align:middle line:84%
shadow element, but it's
more probable that you will.

00:49:22.770 --> 00:49:24.990 align:middle line:84%
And as soon as you do manifest
in the shadow element,

00:49:24.990 --> 00:49:27.750 align:middle line:84%
then it confirms my point of
view that you really are--

00:49:27.750 --> 00:49:29.460 align:middle line:84%
and you know, that
shadowy figure--

00:49:29.460 --> 00:49:29.760 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:49:29.760 --> 00:49:31.176 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: --you
know, ad infinitum.

00:49:31.176 --> 00:49:33.240 align:middle line:84%
But the point is
that if I, instead

00:49:33.240 --> 00:49:36.750 align:middle line:84%
of being caught by that like
one little aspect of you,

00:49:36.750 --> 00:49:39.570 align:middle line:84%
which is the
shadow, if I see you

00:49:39.570 --> 00:49:41.670 align:middle line:84%
in your true nature
in your wholeness--

00:49:41.670 --> 00:49:44.410 align:middle line:84%
and I can only do that if I'm
in touch with my own wholeness.

00:49:44.410 --> 00:49:45.210 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:49:45.210 --> 00:49:47.760 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: Then if I see
your wholeness in that way,

00:49:47.760 --> 00:49:50.760 align:middle line:84%
it actually creates a
bridge for you to more step

00:49:50.760 --> 00:49:51.960 align:middle line:90%
into your wholeness.

00:49:51.960 --> 00:49:54.570 align:middle line:84%
And then the more you are able
to step into your wholeness,

00:49:54.570 --> 00:49:58.170 align:middle line:84%
you see me more in my wholeness,
so you actually help me.

00:49:58.170 --> 00:49:59.630 align:middle line:90%
And it becomes a feedback loop--

00:49:59.630 --> 00:50:00.030 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:50:00.030 --> 00:50:02.196 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: --that's actually
a positive feedback loop.

00:50:02.196 --> 00:50:05.010 align:middle line:84%
We're actually-- we're
like helping each other.

00:50:05.010 --> 00:50:07.950 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And yet, almost
every person gets some kind

00:50:07.950 --> 00:50:10.890 align:middle line:84%
of private little glee
in holding an attitude

00:50:10.890 --> 00:50:15.030 align:middle line:84%
of superiority over another
person or separation with other

00:50:15.030 --> 00:50:17.990 align:middle line:84%
people on some level because
of this stickiness we've been

00:50:17.990 --> 00:50:20.240 align:middle line:90%
through for thousands of years.

00:50:20.240 --> 00:50:22.760 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: Right, but that's
the one way of understanding

00:50:22.760 --> 00:50:25.400 align:middle line:84%
quantum physics is that it's
like shedding a light on that,

00:50:25.400 --> 00:50:28.080 align:middle line:84%
because it's showing that
there's no separation.

00:50:28.080 --> 00:50:28.880 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:50:28.880 --> 00:50:32.010 align:middle line:84%
>> PAUL: That the universe is a
singularity, it's a wholeness.

00:50:32.010 --> 00:50:35.750 align:middle line:84%
There's no-- you know, the
non locality of the universe

00:50:35.750 --> 00:50:40.610 align:middle line:84%
that every part of the
universe is interconnected

00:50:40.610 --> 00:50:42.110 align:middle line:90%
with every other part.

00:50:42.110 --> 00:50:45.620 align:middle line:84%
And so what that means
is that, wait a second,

00:50:45.620 --> 00:50:49.040 align:middle line:84%
if I'm helping you, it helps me,
and we're all in this together

00:50:49.040 --> 00:50:50.250 align:middle line:90%
and we depend on each other.

00:50:50.250 --> 00:50:51.690 align:middle line:90%
We're interdependent.

00:50:51.690 --> 00:50:54.620 align:middle line:84%
And that's kind of why when
I was having-- going back

00:50:54.620 --> 00:50:58.130 align:middle line:84%
to 1981, when I was having
that whole awakening,

00:50:58.130 --> 00:51:00.620 align:middle line:84%
I was having the realization,
oh my God, as artists,

00:51:00.620 --> 00:51:05.630 align:middle line:84%
we can create an art
happening, and you can call it

00:51:05.630 --> 00:51:10.130 align:middle line:84%
sort of this global
awakening in which we're all

00:51:10.130 --> 00:51:13.320 align:middle line:84%
helping each other to
awaken, in other words,

00:51:13.320 --> 00:51:16.130 align:middle line:84%
what I call to dream
ourselves awake.

00:51:16.130 --> 00:51:17.720 align:middle line:90%
To-- it's a conspiracy theory.

00:51:17.720 --> 00:51:20.330 align:middle line:84%
We are conspiring to
co-inspire each other.

00:51:20.330 --> 00:51:22.760 align:middle line:84%
So it's this authentic
conspiracy theory

00:51:22.760 --> 00:51:26.330 align:middle line:84%
that we're activating the
genius, the collective genius,

00:51:26.330 --> 00:51:28.730 align:middle line:84%
in each other, and
that's evolutionary

00:51:28.730 --> 00:51:31.850 align:middle line:84%
and that's what's available
to us as a species.

00:51:31.850 --> 00:51:35.870 align:middle line:84%
And quantum physics is actually
pointing exactly at that,

00:51:35.870 --> 00:51:38.010 align:middle line:90%
if we interpret it correctly.

00:51:38.010 --> 00:51:41.390 align:middle line:84%
And that's pointing out, well,
we have it within our creative

00:51:41.390 --> 00:51:44.730 align:middle line:84%
genius, within our power to
actually change the world,

00:51:44.730 --> 00:51:47.201 align:middle line:84%
and not just in sort of new
agey, abstract, woo-woo way--

